			===================================================
				           2. Platform Independent
			===================================================
=> A Platform is nothing but type of OS Being Used(OS Acts as Resource Allocation and De-allocation
Manager).
=> In IT, we have 2 Types of Programming Languages. They are

                1. Platform Dependent Language.
                2. Platform Independent Language.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Platform Dependent Language
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



Examples: C,C++
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. Platform Independent Language
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



Examples: Java, PYTHON